    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>START YOUR 2 STROKE ENGINES AND PREPARE TO BATHE IN THE PIXELATED BLOOD OF THE UNHOLY HORDES!</strong> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is Carnage Kart X?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carnage Kart X™ is a retro-inspired Hack n' Slash n' Kart game combining hand-drawn 2D pixel art and 3D gameplay like it's 1996! Use your weapons and driving skill as a Knight of the Kart to survive swarms of fiendish ghouls and horrendous horrors who would like nothing more than to see you join the ranks of the dead!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180270/extras/74bcfaa2c2a7f6730b2fe8882144bc0d.poster.avif?t=1761261702\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180270/extras/74bcfaa2c2a7f6730b2fe8882144bc0d.webm?t=1761261702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180270/extras/74bcfaa2c2a7f6730b2fe8882144bc0d.mp4?t=1761261702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Classic Mode</strong>, you must endure 5 minutes in each stage <i><strong>if you can</strong></i> while taking on challenges to swell your coffers and increase your chances at bonus bullion! Use your weapons and mechanics to drift, grind, boost, and slaughter your way around the stages!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And introducing <strong>Colosseum Mode,</strong> where you can experience Rogue-Like gameplay, slashing and upgrading your weapons, kart, and skills within a single session! This mode even supports 2 player couch co-op so you can slaughter zombies with your friend!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180270/extras/d5c66c2bfcbf3bec93897a7d374d976f.poster.avif?t=1761261702\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180270/extras/d5c66c2bfcbf3bec93897a7d374d976f.webm?t=1761261702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180270/extras/d5c66c2bfcbf3bec93897a7d374d976f.mp4?t=1761261702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Old School Kart Racing!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Live long enough to play the bonus round at the end of each stage and enjoy a classic kart race with the local foes! Put them in their place, preferably while staying in 1st, and earn even more Gold and Soul Shards, the currencies used for unlocking new weapons, sub-weapons, and upgrading your kart stats! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180270/extras/5f0c379ad208d4c7db2677dcec6a4eec.poster.avif?t=1761261702\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180270/extras/5f0c379ad208d4c7db2677dcec6a4eec.webm?t=1761261702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180270/extras/5f0c379ad208d4c7db2677dcec6a4eec.mp4?t=1761261702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tested on the Steam Deck!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is playable on the Steam Deck! (it just takes longer for small indie games to be verified by Steam)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180270/extras/e634bf4bead66d69763169184d145eb6.poster.avif?t=1761261702\" width=640 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180270/extras/e634bf4bead66d69763169184d145eb6.webm?t=1761261702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So adjust thine helm, gauntlets at 10 and 2, and prepare thyself for battle in the best game to ever put a sword on a go-kart! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180270/extras/1b0cb60618be6470525cf1da9ca0875b.apng?t=1761261702\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180270/extras/1b0cb60618be6470525cf1da9ca0875b.poster.avif?t=1761261702\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=112 /></picture></span></p>",
